column2: SELECT TOP ALL a.OBJID AS OBJID, a.RA AS RA, a.DEC AS DEC, ph.objID AS sdssid, ph.ra AS RA_sdss, ph.dec AS DEC_sdss, ph.mode AS mode, ph.probPSF AS probPSF, ph.modelMag_u AS umag, ph.modelMag_g AS gmag, ph.modelMag_r AS rmag, ph.modelMag_i AS imag, ph.modelMag_z AS zmag, ph.modelMagErr_u AS e_umag, ph.modelMagErr_g AS e_gmag, ph.modelMagErr_r AS e_rmag, ph.modelMagErr_i AS e_imag, ph.modelMagErr_z AS e_zmag, n.distance AS angDist into mydb.AKARIx3#SDSS_ugriz_crac from MyDB.akari AS a OUTER APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (a.RA, a.DEC, #) AS n LEFT JOIN PhotoObjAll as ph ON n.objid = ph.objid
